Nezha Regragui (Arabic: نزهة الركراكي, a mụrụ n'abalị 17, ọnwa Disemba, afọ 1957) bụ onye Morocco na-eme ihe nkiri, TV na ihe nkiri. Regragui esonyewo n'ọtụtụ egwuregwu na ihe nkiri, gụnyere Goodbye Mothers
Ọ bụkwa onye a ma ama maka ịlụ onye na-agụ egwu Bachir Abdou ma bụrụkwa nne na nna onye na-abụ egwu Moroccan Saad Lamjarred.
